    All three files are also streamed to the controller in real time and accessible from the job detail page in the web UI without needing to SSH into the agent host.
  </p>

  <h3>System Log (JSON format)</h3>
  <p>The agent's main structured log (written to <code>&#123;log_dir&#125;/agent.log</code> and stdout of the systemd unit) uses the following JSON schema:</p>
  <pre><code>&#123;
  "time":    "2025-11-14T08:32:01.452Z",
  "level":   "info",
  "msg":     "job assigned",
  "job_id":  "a3f8c1d2-...",
